Text: Running a little late. Weren’t sure where to go, but found our way!Stephen, park at Salford Station Road and Wolford Road. Look for the yellow school buses, that will take you to the festival. Or you can walk 1/2 mile to get there. See you soon!
Okay sorry for the confusion. Just text me when you’re in and I’ll come find you

Sounds good.
The shuttle bus just arrived.
I’m walking through the tents and parking now soon to be at artist checkin.
Ok we are at artist checkin
I’m going to hang back here and get ready for the set. I’ll come out right after and we can hang more. We play until 8:30. Did you get a good place to sit?
Heading down to grab a seat now
Got great seats right in front
Loved “Got great seats right in front ”
